  "source_note": "Keeper Rulebook Chapter 4 Skill List (p.56 / PDF idx 55). Each entry maps a canonical skill name to its base chance percentage, its specialization group (or null), whether it is modern-era only (Omega marker in the rulebook), and whether it is uncommon (T marker - not printed on the standard investigator sheet). Group skills (G) are broken into separate specializations; this file lists each specialization individually with its group set to the parent skill name (e.g. 'Fighting', 'Firearms'). Source: chapter 4, p.56.",
